OL,3,CChief Minister addresses concerns over
OL,4,Cgas leaks and promises action
OL,6,F"The Government needs to be sure that
OL,7,Fit has the power and authority to hold
OL,8,Fthe gas company to account and force
OL,9,Fit to take actions more quickly than
OL,10,Fin the past."
OL,12,FRecent gas leaks and the ongoing
OL,13,Finvestigation into the Haut du Mont
OL,14,Fexplosion which killed ten people led
OL,15,Fto a number of questions in the
OL,16,FChamber about safety concerns.
