OL,3,CChief Minister addresses concerns over
OL,4,Cgas leaks and promises action
OL,6,FDeputy Farnham said: "Safety of the
OL,7,Fnetwork remains a main issue and the
OL,8,FChief Executive (of Island Energy)
OL,9,Fconfirmed that the company is
OL,10,Faccelerating its renewal programme and
OL,11,Fdoubling its investment in gas
OL,12,Finfrastructure.
OL,14,F"In any sphere of life, you can never
OL,15,Fguarantee that accidents won't happen
OL,16,Fbut we're doing everything in our
OL,17,Fpower to reduce the risk."
