OL,6,FThose comments have not allayed the
OL,7,Ffears of some States Members as Deputy
OL,8,FPhilip Ozouf stated: "I don't like
OL,9,Fsaying it but I worry that there is
OL,10,Fanother accident waiting to happen.
OL,11,FNothing that I've heard from the Chief
OL,12,FMinister is going to help my
OL,13,Fconstituents and those across the
OL,14,Fisland.
OL,16,F"I'm afraid words are simply not going
OL,17,Fto be enough when there's another
OL,18,Ffatality which could happen, it's a
OL,19,Freal risk."
