OL,3,CChief Minister addresses concerns over
OL,4,Cgas leaks and promises action
OL,6,FDeputy Farnham says Island Energy is
OL,7,Ffollowing UK best practice on gas
OL,8,Fdisconnections following "a thorough
OL,9,Freview".
OL,11,FHe added: "Since the new Chief
OL,12,FExecutive has taken over, we've seen a
OL,13,Fmarked improvement in their
OL,14,Fcommunication with the Government,
OL,15,Fofficials and the public.
OL,17,F"We need to see this improvement to
OL,18,Fthe gas infrastructure and increased
OL,19,Fexpenditure continue to be accelerated
OL,20,Fso we can ensure our gas network is
OL,21,Fsafe."
