OL,3,CChief Minister addresses concerns over
OL,4,Cgas leaks and promises action
OL,6,FDeputy Farnham praised islanders'
OL,7,Fproactiveness in reporting recent gas
OL,8,Fleaks and underlined safety is the top
OL,9,Fpriority.
OL,11,FHe explained: "The public has been far
OL,12,Fmore aware in reporting even the most
OL,13,Fminor potential smell of gas and I'm
OL,14,Fpleased that's happening because it
OL,15,Fmeans we're being careful and a lot
OL,16,Fmore mindful.
