OL,3,CChief Minister addresses concerns over
OL,4,Cgas leaks and promises action
OL,6,F"We're carrying out evacuations now,
OL,7,Fregardless of where there is a problem
OL,8,Fbut there might not be a risk of
OL,9,Fexplosion, to make sure that public
OL,10,Fsafety comes first."
OL,12,FThe Chief Minister also confirmed that
OL,13,Fan open forum will be held as soon as
OL,14,Fpossible between the new Island Energy
OL,15,FChief Executive Graeme Millar and
OL,16,FStates members so they can ask
OL,17,Fquestions directly.
