OL,3,CChief Minister addresses concerns over
OL,4,Cgas leaks and promises action
OL,6,FDeputy Farnham says more than 1,000
OL,7,Fmeasurements of drains and tunnels
OL,8,Facross Jersey have been taken by the
OL,9,FInfrastructure Department over the
OL,10,Fpast two years to act as an "early
OL,11,Fwarning system" and reduce the risk of
OL,12,Ffurther gas leaks.
