OL,3,CChief Minister addresses concerns over
OL,4,Cgas leaks and promises action
OL,6,FHe explained: "In a simple world, we
OL,7,Fmight say let's just eliminate the use
OL,8,Fof gas altogether but of course,
OL,9,Fthat's not easy or straightforward and
OL,10,Fwould take time. The hospitality
OL,11,Findustry relies on gas and then
OL,12,Fthere's the capacity to transfer all
OL,13,Fof those businesses to our electricity
OL,14,Fgrid which could take many years to
OL,15,Fachieve."
OL,17,FIsland Energy has told ITV News it
OL,18,Fwill not comment further and said that
OL,19,Fthe Chief Minister's responses reflect
OL,20,Fits position.
